SUMMARY:Social Clubs
DESCRIPTION:February 2026 \n\n\n\nTuesday\n2/3\n4:00 PM – 7:00 PM\nDeliza’s Pizza – Boonton\n\n\nThursday\n2/5\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” Black History Trivia ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nSaturday\n   2/7\n11:30 AM – 1:00 PM \n Rockaway Mall \n\n\nMonday\n2/9\n6:00 PM -7:30 PM\nOpen Mic – Succasunna\n\n\nTuesday \n2/10\n4:00 PM – 7:00 PM\nTJ Maxx – Rockaway \n\n\nThursday\n2/12\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” Valentine’s Day Celebration ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nTuesday\n2/17\n4:00 PM – 7:00 PM\nBurlington/ Marshalls – East Hanover \n\n\nThursday\n2/19\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n “Thursday’s” Karaoke ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\nSaturday \n2/21\n11:00 AM – 12:30 PM \nHobby Lobby – East Hanover \n\n\nTuesday\n2/24\n4:00 PM – 7:00 PM\nBarnes & Noble – Morris Plains \n\n\nThursday\n2/26\n6:30 PM – 8:00 PM\n“Thursday’s” Word Search ~ ESSEX OFFICE  \n\n\n\n  \n  \nSPACE IS LIMITED!! \nTo register or for more information\, please contact:\nYecenia Revolorio – 973-334-3496 ext. 514\nWeekdays 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM \nLight refreshments will be served.\nPrizes available for winners. \nActivity is subject to change and/or cancel.
URL:https://www.mhainspire.org/event/social-clubs-30/2026-03-06/
CATEGORIES:Social Clubs
END:VEVENT
