SUMMARY:Family and Consumer Connection Group
DESCRIPTION:Family and Consumer Connection Group: A professionally facilitated group where\nfamilies and consumers come together to discuss and problem-solve challenges in a\nsupportive environment. Goals of the group include providing support\, improving\ncommunication\, and strengthening socialization. This group meets on the 1st and \n3rd Tuesday of the month from 3:00pm to 4:15pm Participation requires an\norientation process. If you wish to participate in The Family and Consumer\nConnection group\, please reach out to Eileen Strungis at (973) 509-9777\, x 123\, or\nemail her at estrungis@mhainspire.org
URL:https://www.mhainspire.org/event/family-and-consumer-connection-group-2-2/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Virtual
CATEGORIES:Support Groups
END:VEVENT
